Description.Display: This package contains the driver for the Intel Thunderbolt Controller. Thunderbolt driver allows you to connect devices such as storage devices, monitors, and other peripherals to the system, by using the Thunderbolt port.

This package contains the driver for the Intel AX210, AX201, AX200, 9560, 9260, 8265, and 3165 wireless cards. Wireless drivers help your operating system to communicate with wireless devices such as wireless cards and network interface controllers.

This package contains the driver for the Intel Management Engine Components Installer. This driver installs Intel Management Engine Interface, Serial Over LAN driver, Local Manageability Service, Intel Converged Security and Manageability Engine (CSME), Windows Management Instrumentation (WMI) provider, Intel Management Security Status application, and Intel Capability Licensing Service Client. This update also addresses the Intel Technical Advisory INTEL-TA-00459.

This package contains the driver for the Intel AX200, AX201, 9560, 9260, and 3165 Bluetooth cards. Bluetooth driver is the software that helps your operating system to communicate with Bluetooth devices.
